'''''Bokhandlaren som slutade bada''''' (''The Bookseller Who Gave Up Bathing'', 1937) is a novel by [[Fritiof Nilsson Piraten]]. The book would be adapted as a film<ref>[http://sverigesradio.se/sida/artikel.aspx?programid=1111&artikel=5352353 {{sv}} Sveriges Radio]</ref> and placed on [[Världsbiblioteket]].<ref>[http://dagensbok.com/2009/09/23/varldsbiblioteket/ {{sv}} Dagensbok.com]</ref> The film version was directed by [[Jarl Kulle]] and concerns a bachelor, and book-seller, who marries a mysterious widow.<ref>[http://www.sky.com/tv/movie/the-bookseller-who-gave-up-bathing-1968 Sky plc]</ref>

