'''''Vat jou goed en trek!''''' Is an Afrikaans home renovation show on South Africa's satellite channel Kyknet.

''Vat jou goed en trek!'' is a home renovation show that helps South African families, struggling  to sell their homes. A team consisting of an interior designer, a landscape architect, a general contractor and a leading real estate agent meet with home owners and have 72 hours to renovate three areas of the property, dress the property and show it to potential buyers. ''Vat jou goed en trek!'' is currently on its fourth season and is produced by Conrey Entertainment for the Afrikaans channel Kyknet. The show is presented by Henck Conrey and stars Lara Fourie (A-Z Design Boutique) and Kevin Brider (Po10tail Construction).

